==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[steam]] [[engine]]}}

# A [[piston engine]] driven by steam (as contrasted, for example, with a [[steam turbine]]).
# Any machine that performs mechanical work using steam from an external source as its primary working fluid.
# {{UK}} A [[steam locomotive]].
# {{rfd-redundant}} A [[heat engine]] that uses steam as its primary working fluid to do [[mechanical]] [[work]].

